name: Swirl
description: 12" x 12" felted "painting". This piece is already secured in a cottage white wooden frame and ready to hang on your walls.

name: Rise to Raise
description:
"Rise to Raise" suggest the potential for new growth, the sun rising and seedlings coming to sprout. Nature IS (not vs.) Nuture and all it takes is a little warmth for us to reach new heights. 

This brand new felted art piece is 12" x 12" x 4" (3" gallery wrapped stretcher plus + 1" felted elements). Ready to hang!

Made with merino, harrisville, romney wools, 9 small glass marbles and merino yard. I needle-felted it onto craft felt for stability and then used wet-felting techniques to secure and soften the image. Once dry, it was stretched over an upcycled canvas stretcher to truly give it a professional art finish. Signed on back!
